--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
bg/field_of_values.m
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Adapted from the Matrix Computation Toolbox by N. J. Higham.

  N. J. Higham, Accuracy and Stability of Numerical Algorithms,
  SIAM, Philadelphia, PA, 2nd ed., 2002.
  https://people.maths.manchester.ac.uk/higham/mctoolbox/

Original function name: fv (field of values / numerical range).
Used here in modified form (plotting branch removed, filename changed).
The Matrix Computation Toolbox is made freely available for non-commercial use.
Please cite Higham's book if you use results that depend on this routine.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
srg_hard.m  (algorithm)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
The hard-SRG algorithm implemented in srg_hard.m is translated and adapted
from SrgTools.jl by Julius P. J. Krebbekx.

  J. P. J. Krebbekx, "SrgTools.jl", https://github.com/Krebbekx/SrgTools.jl
  Reference: arXiv:2511.17297

